    "Name": "Ursus",
    "Details": "The Ursus 1 is a flexible defender that mounts a variety of weapons to engage enemies at all ranges. Its weakness is in its lack of long-range capability, though the ER Large Laser and LRM-10 are respectable for a 'Mech its size. For closer work, it uses two ER Medium Lasers, two Medium Pulse Lasers, and a SRM-6 launcher. This blistering hail of weapons fire is generally effective for an Inner Sphere heavy 'Mech, so the Ursus compares favorably to the designs that it is expected to stand up against.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Distracting</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.1</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Right Lower</color>",
